Install Eclipse 3.2 SDK. Setup whatever proxies are required and install all of Calisto using the Update Manager. Restart Eclipse.
Window->Show View->Error Log 
Start with the Java Perspective
File->New->Project->Java Project. Name it jp. Finish
MB2 on jp ->Open in New Window
In the new window navigate back to the workspace (not really neccessary)
Window->Open Perspective->Other->J2EE
File->New->Project->Java Project. Name it jp2. Finish.
This step is important. Select NO when prompted to changed to the Java Perspective.
